QuestData.Title: No Troll Left Behind
QuestData.Description:
Dis is de primary port for de Zandalari fleet. Thankfully most of our ships were out when de mogu came, but Rastari is still an active fortification for de city.
De mogu did not land on abandoned shores, $c. Dere are all manner of brave warriors stationed here, fighting for their lives.
Take dis whistle and rally all you can. Our warriors will hear its scream and know dat dey are not alone.
